reviewText:
- purely an exploration game with repetitive tasks;
- beautiful desert/rock sceneries;
- virtually non-existent story (you have to build a car);
- typical casual strike/heavy/parry combat system on foot;
- satisfying car combat;
- minor non-critical technical issues, solid performance on a laptop.
All in all, might or might not be a good waste of time for you. Not a masterpiece, but a solid unsophisticated game.
8/10
